{
  "stem": "19895.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were not starving.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because somehow there-- if there was food for one family, there was food for the other family.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, and people were making good money on selling food to Jews.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were overpaying for prices.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And everybody had savings, everybody had jewelry, which they sold.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And if money found its source, the food arrived.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were not starving in those last days before they were rounding us up and taking us away.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was in the messenger service.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And whatever that-- an interesting thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes, you reminded me of something.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "People were standing in line on the street, to get papers from the Jewish Council that the Jewish Council releases them from being part of the Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And with that paper, they showed up at Christian organizations for asking legally to be admitted to another religion, conversions.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And hundreds of people were standing on street, in front of the Jewish Council's entrance, who were trying to get those papers, to be released from being part of the Jewish community and have-- and the other religions, they wanted to have these official papers from them.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I looked on them that these people are to me kind of selling out their beliefs and religion.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I understand now that probably many of them were mixed marriages, people from mixed marriages who, who wanted to save their life.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were going to do anything, including to convert.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But that was another activity, which I witnessed as being part of this messenger service in the Budapest Jewish Council.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And even that question came up in our own family-- if that would do any good, and should we try that ourself.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my father firmly objected to it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I firmly object to it.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
